casebody.data:
No. 524. Norfolk & Western Railway Company, Petitioner, v. Louella May, Administratrix, etc. January 13, 1908. Mr. Theodore W, Reath and Mr. Joseph I. Doran for petitioner. Mr. Clement Manly for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
